<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<h2 id="completed-inspections">Completed inspections</h2>
<p>The bracketed dates show when the reports were sent to the Home Secretary, who aims to publish within 8 weeks of receipt.</p>

<ol>
  <li>Clandestine Entrants (13 March 2020)</li>
  <li>Use of interpreters (14 May 2020)</li>
  <li>Resettlement Schemes: VPRS, VCRS and Community Sponsorship (14 September 2020)</li>
  <li>Disruption and prosecution of perpetrators of modern slavery (16 September 2020)</li>
  <li>Inspection of the Home Office’s Country of Origin Information products relating to Sexual Orientation and Gender Identity or Expression, September 2020. (13 October 2020)</li>
</ol>

<h2 id="live-inspections">Live inspections</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Sanctions and Penalties</li>
  <li>Presenting Officers</li>
  <li>Intelligence</li>
  <li>Asylum casework</li>
  <li>Adults at Risk 2</li>
  <li>E-gates</li>
  <li>Front-end services</li>
  <li>Freight</li>
  <li>EU Settlement Scheme 3</li>
</ol>

